Katya looked at Kup.

Katya: You know our forces and you know the Predacons'. I leave the
decision whether to go or not in your hands.

Ragnar understood what it took Katya to give command to Kup, but he
knew it was in Vlad's best interest.

Owlhawk shifted uneasily on his feet. He wanted to bust some Vok, but
his scanners detected only residual Vok presence around. Had she been
destroyed?
